QuestData.Title: Changing Seasons
QuestData.Description:
I appreciate you saving me again, but we should do something to prevent this from happening to anyone else.
So long as that Wicker Man stands, it will attract more like Autumnvale to it.
We should destroy it! Are you with me?
QuestData.LogDescription: Burn the Wicker Man in Autumnvale.
QuestData.CompletionText: The Wicker Man must be destroyed!
QuestData.RewardText:
Well I've certainly learned my lesson.
Thank you, friend. I will return to Boralus with my parents now.
Here, take this for your troubles.
